ppa-purge (0.2.5) karmic; urgency=low

  * New syntax: ppa-purge [options] <ppa> (not the other way)
  * New option -s for repository server hostname
  * Accept the ppa:owner/name URI as well
  * use dpkg --print-architecture and drop depends on dpkg-dev
  * debian/control: Architecture: all
  * debian/control: update to Standards 3.8.3 (no changes needed)

 -- Tormod Volden <debian.tormod@gmail.com>  Wed, 30 Sep 2009 00:58:31 +0200

